				<main role="main" class=""><article class="main-content"><h1 class="">Ajo Unified School District #15</h1>
        <h2 class="">Where everyone graduates college and career ready</h2>
        <p class="">Welcome to Ajo Unified School District #15, where everyone graduates college and career ready. Our schools provide a safe, empowering learning environment for PreK through 12th grade students in the historic, peaceful town of Ajo, Arizona. </p>
<p class="">Thank you for taking the time to visit our online home. We are happy to provide you with information about our district, our schools, and the excellent programs and services we offer our students. Go, Red Raiders!</p>
        
        <h2 class="">A Message from Our Superintendent</h2>
        <p class="">Dear Ajo Parents &amp; Students,</p>
<p class="">I’m very pleased to introduce myself as the superintendent of Ajo Unified School District #15. I find it to be a privilege to work with the students of Ajo.  I invite you to visit the Superintendent page to learn more about me and my background as an educator. </p>
<p class="">Ours is a small learning community, and we are all dedicated to the same thing—your child’s education. Whether our students want to pursue higher education or careers after high school, our schools prepare them for success from preschool through high school graduation. Together, our administrative team, faculty, and staff put an extraordinary amount of time and effort into making sure your children’s needs come first. Our students are why we exist as a district.  This school was created for students, not adults.</p>
<p class="">Parent involvement and strong communication between school and home is a priority in all of our schools, so please don’t hesitate to contact us with your questions or concerns.</p>
        <p class="">Sincerely,</p>
        <div class="signature">Dr. Robert Dooley</div>
